game.name: Nut Rush
game.description:
The squirrel is feeling so hungry and looking for acorns. In this extremely popular adventure game for kids, you will have to help the squirrel to gather the maximum possible acorns to fulfill his true desires. Remember, the better techniques and tricks you will use to jump him over the obstacles and hindrances that come on his way, the easier it has become for him to reach his home safely. To ensure your victory in each level of this awesome adventure game ? Nut Rush, all you need to do is put your skills and reflexes to the test. 

In this highly challenging and interesting game for children from different age groups, you have to jump perfectly from one branch to branch. No need to lose your concentration while doing this activity otherwise, your character might fall from the true. Proper hand-to-eye coordination, patience and good focus will help to make sure that you will complete all the levels of this cool free online game. You will surely have huge fun while collecting food among countless trees for the squirrel. 

This animal adventure game will allow you to jump high and low to land on the wooden platform. Roll up your sleeves, help the squirrel to eat the acorns and reach home conveniently in Nut Rush. Amazing graphics and easy control are the major features of this run and jump platforming game. Play this flash game in your browser today and enjoy the control on a cute squirrel!
